our journey starts with a consultation appointment where Ashley assesses your hair, discusses options, and takes measurements. If you move forward, a separate installation appointment is scheduled. Installation times vary by method and volume. Ashley also provides guidance on maintenance, care, and move-up scheduling to keep your extensions looking natural."}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoBlock","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoItem","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoLabel","children":"Pricing"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoValue","children":"Consultation required for pricing"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoDivider"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoItem","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoLabel","children":"Duration"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoValue","children":"Varies by method"}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__cta","children":["$","a",null,{"href":"/book/consult","className":"Button-module__zVQJKW__button Button-module__zVQJKW__primary Button-module__zVQJKW__fullWidth","children":"Start a Consultation"}]}],["$","aside",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__ashleyNote","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__noteLabel","children":"A note from Ashley"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__noteText","children":"Extensions are deeply personal — they can be genuinely life-changing for the right person. I require a consultation because I need to see your hair, understand your lifestyle, and make sure we choose the right method. I will never install extensions that would compromise your natural hair."}]]}]]}]}],[["$","link","0",{"rel":"stylesheet","href":"/_next/static/chunks/0~ww8ls-m-185.css","precedence":"next"}],"$L3","$L4"],"$L5"]}],"isPartial":false,"staleTime":30